Date: Wed, 20 Aug 2025 15:26:41 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:wifi:nl80211/mac80211: Refactor the ttlm
 code

Refactor the advertised ttlm APIs and move the structure definitions
before ap setting to use the same in start ap context.

Signed-off-by: Shwetha G K <kshwetha@qti.qualcomm.com>
